Actress, Tonto Dikeh is in a celebratory mood as her son, King Andre, turns seven today February 17. Posting lovely photos of herself and her son on her Instagram page, the excited mum thanked him for making ??Fatherhood/Motherhood” a beautiful ride. ??Loving you comes easy because YOU ARE LOVE.. @kingandre_dikeh Thank you for making Fatherhood/Motherhood a beautiful Ride.. Thank you for choosing me, Thank you for all the beauty you bring to my Life. I cherish and Adore you,My World” See the lovely photos Tonto shared below?